# Excludes for railway up.  Railway honours this in addition to .gitignore.
# .gitignore already excludes node_modules, .yarn caches, dist, etc.
# Drop the .git history (385 MB) and packages whose source isn't needed
# by the Twenty server/worker Dockerfile build (only docs/marketing/etc).
# Do NOT exclude any package referenced from package.json's workspaces[]
# without also pruning yarn.lock — otherwise yarn install in the container
# loses transitive type/dev deps.

